Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞的少年 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時走在兩條道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一條是找出殺母兇手 這一通往『過去』的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一條則是 創造妹妹娜娜莉能夠幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一通往『未來』的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在魯魯修凝視『過去』和『未來』之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他自己能夠選擇『現在』的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是世界的毀滅呢 還是世界的構築呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 17
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}騎    士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 毛已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺了… 自己的父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你一個人的秘密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫『桐原』吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以自己的死來對他們進行勸解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了壓制堅持徹底抗戰的主戰派
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本首相樞木玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為需要這樣一個故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是對日本 還是對布里塔尼亞來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 我早就有些疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他原本不是這種優先他人的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺死異母兄弟就已經那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀把父親… 而且還是在年僅10歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼獨自一人承擔著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 臉不要亂動啊 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 視線要再往下一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過向下了 上去一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情和之前完全不同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 和剛才完全不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是憂鬱的表情比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 不是挺好的嗎 傻傻的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一節課不是數學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是藝術周嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是克洛維斯殿下的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術周的第一天 將會舉行克洛維斯紀念美術館的落成典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望尤菲米婭殿下從這些畫中選出得獎作品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:04:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據調查 那幅畫的畫家有四分之一的ELEVEN血統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一開始就不要展出不就好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面功夫也是需要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那幅 請看一下這邊的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是尼古拉公爵公子的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章魚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個是… 總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們有京都的介紹信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是… 『四聖劍』!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我單刀直入了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能借助你們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂中校被俘虜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我們逃走而選擇了自我犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 答應下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之騎士團是『正義的使者』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好奇怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合方法用B-13
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把KnightMare分散 運往18號方向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓迪特哈魯特來指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也傳達給預定集合的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 中華聯邦那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經全部重新安排了 不必太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的利用價值改變了的話 會妨礙計劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是期盼已久的湊齊兩個棋子之日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 要把另一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是籐堂鏡志朗的處刑日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必到場監督了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟日本解放戰線已不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行刑就讓那個人來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總督
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美術館那邊不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典禮是下午開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NAC那邊說 石川那裡有不穩的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幕後活動的不是EU就是中華聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有確認『鋼髏』出現的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[鋼髏:中華聯邦的KnightMare]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這也是平定北陸的大好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓達爾頓留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情都可以找他商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就提過的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的騎士就從這裡面挑選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪個都很優秀 家世也很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 冬天庭院裡的池塘會結冰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去溜冰後還被哥哥訓了一頓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木神社也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是很小的池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們經常去釣蝲蛄… 啊 就是小龍蝦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龍蝦… 能釣起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用線綁住青蛙的腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 青蛙就是『咯羅咯羅』那麼叫的青蛙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用日語說起來是『Kero Kero』這麼叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Kero Kero』?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 『Kero Kero』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果按計劃進行下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我將不在娜娜莉的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也有過毛的教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一 需要有能夠保護娜娜莉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉能成為他的生存意義的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對那個人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伊德說有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微借用朱雀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了已經不要緊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人已經不會再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來後我有事想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的 非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 聽起來好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼回頭再說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀也成為別人的依靠了呢 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得朱雀怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 最喜歡的還是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉 我先走一步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啦 你這薄情的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這次美術館的建設
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說ELEVEN的公司被排除在外?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 關於這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事仍在調查中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請恕我們不便作答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問尤菲米婭殿下政治上的事也沒有用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是InterState的格裡曼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有傳聞表示您最近要決定騎士的人選?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 是的 騎士…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次的提問限定在有關美術館的範圍之內哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了配線不要絞在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 這和『無賴』是不同的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題嗎 和黑之騎士團聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他方法能救出籐堂中校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是京都的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且說會借給我們新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 主義和主張還是有所不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並非是民族主義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑣碎的小事還是等救出中校再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂先生所在的地方 亦是我的安身地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩死了 一股腦塞進去得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離出擊已經沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更溫柔地對待它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它比你們的東西要纖細百倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 你是誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於你的傳聞我是聽了不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此 拉克夏塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前經常在網絡上看到關於你的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於醫療控制論(Cybernetics)的報導
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡提以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從京都帶來的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子真的能提高聯動性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會提高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高的是生存率
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死刑執行人更換了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樞木朱雀准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧 是熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要寫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是柯內莉婭殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但手續還是不能少的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死刑執行人更換 是特例中的特例
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這… 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可以從文書地獄中解放了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 我們現在就來救你!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊 這架『月下』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟『無賴』真是有天壤之別
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和附屬武器的聯動還是不夠完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 會不會是線路的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信號識別有0.07的偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都的老爺子們應該送些更好的部件來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被劫走前先解決掉 這是上頭的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼遺言嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經捨棄過的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼值得留戀的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你的生命就… 交給我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂鏡志朗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在7年前的戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一讓布里塔尼亞灰頭土臉的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『嚴島的奇跡』嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也期待著我的奇跡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是什麼奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是情報收集基礎上的戰術成功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想得到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決心侍奉的主君片瀨少將已經不在人世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別天真了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須負起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡的責任!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起其它地區明顯要強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AREA-11的抵抗運動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由於日本在尚有餘力的情況下就投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為『嚴島的奇跡』這一夢想的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有讓人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們總是抱有『奇跡』這一幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正是因為如此 Refrain才會蔓延的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掙扎吧! 籐堂!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼狽地掙扎到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再死去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到『奇跡的籐堂』這一名號徹底粉碎為止!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這樣日本人才能接受戰敗的事實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了民眾 這是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我會讓夢想成為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來就請尤菲米婭皇女殿下選出得獎作品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛上這朵花的作品將會被評選為大獎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 籐堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉手之勞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協助ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殲滅這裡的殘餘兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 所有的條件都具備了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉的騎士也選好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那傢伙會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的問題居然自己跑了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該做決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調布基地出事了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很善戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 挺厲害的嘛 敵人的新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 塞希爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是結果論
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的全部家當只有一輛卡車 還真是幸運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說預算全用在Lancelot上了吧 就結果來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓ZERO頭痛不已的白色機甲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了 七對一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很頑強啊 那個叫Lancelot的KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 又躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊! 白騎士!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 全軍出動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援樞木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將剿滅恐怖分子的消息報導出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 有這架機體的情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有辦法對付他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡希望能按照我的指示行事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部人拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種速度和操控確實很具威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的行動有一定的規律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的攻擊會從正面進行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且絕對不會瞄準要害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為防止之後被攻擊 它會立刻移動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面攻擊若被躲過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解讀它的移動數據
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-57
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下 下一個動作是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向後移動拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐標是 X-23
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的『三段刺』被看穿了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了! 沒有逃脫裝置!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒裝上去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朱雀…嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO! 指示!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給下一步的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來 所有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 那個!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ELEVEN 應該是叫樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克洛維斯殿下那時的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼ELEVEN會在KnightMare裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終止影像! 不許繼續!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手! 朱雀!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂先生!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不惜歪曲世理也要苟活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失望了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就按照預定把我處決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能在那種地方啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該留在娜娜莉的身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是為此才來這裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然淪為甘於現狀的沒出息的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使否定現在的社會也沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該承認它 並且得到改變它的力量才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你就按那條路走下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論成功還是失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不竭盡全力就什麼也得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點對於國家和個人都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 要抓住他嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 毀滅白色機甲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下! 要等ZERO的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙波大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用『旋回活殺自在陣』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手! 現在還…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從四周同時進行的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是絕對躲不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木准尉 Harken Booster解除!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密碼是我最愛吃的東西!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣的作戰方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈 你從左面繞過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要繼續戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的已經達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用3號路線…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻撤退!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏不了的戰鬥和敗北的戰鬥是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來深有心得呢 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開干擾煙霧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 他們逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊退了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 幹的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叛徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不追
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為同是ELEVEN吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得以一對七還能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米婭殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來回答剛才的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有人問我是否決定了騎士人選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選為騎士的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡的那位…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木朱雀准尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂先生 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO不出來麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對… 叫他也沒回應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:21:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的敵人?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該保護娜娜莉的男人 卻成了尤菲米婭的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說黑之騎士團的陣容已趨於穩固
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:24:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我能夠下決心嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不顧全大局嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓世界變成我所期望的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,330)}{\fn方正综艺_GBK}STAGE 18
